tid":1782663,"uid":318082,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"屌 收撚皮<br />\n班鄉音廢老擲磚就沒人拉"},{"pid":"9ae2ae87aa9aedfc18e94ed5a0cb3487ffecef25","tid":1782663,"uid":37869,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂】現場有警員掟磚？ 高級警司：無可厚非可以接受<br />\n<br />\n2016年大年初二旺角發生騷亂，本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦及「美國隊長」容偉業等人被控暴動罪，案件繼續審理。當日置身現場的高級警司莫慶榮出庭作供，辯方盤問時播出當晚疑有警員掟磚片段，質疑莫明知警員掟磚卻未有阻止，同屬參與暴動。莫不同意，堅稱當晚沒留意到有警員掟磚。辯方追問，警方掟磚是否可取？莫直言當時警方遭受生命威脅，面對暴徒投擲「磚雨」，警方還手掟磚絕對是「無可厚非，可以接受」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181231/59089645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59089645&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=de272208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59089645&h=c9875692\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181231/59089645</a>"},{"pid":"461bb2b2d239d45d7863cfe49c836960e54c3a5a","tid":1782663,"uid":78122,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"係咪冇掟傷人就可以當冇事先"},{"pid":"1c7dee214c3a017e64b6b595d575d20298692ad5","tid":1782663,"uid":271161,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"明明自己友掟中自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf33b1755aee3d75c404684502fd83d1470741b","tid":1782663,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"咁即係TK啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98133a1b88fcb0c9706918ed18b8b3348d03e8df","tid":1782663,"uid":121146,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"影唔到  又可以拉三個後生仔<br />\n乜後生係原罪黎？"},{"